column5: Hey guys,  I'll be heading up to the Collingwood area this weekend and I was wondering if there is any fishing or ice fishing in the area? Any help would be appreciated since I'm not familiar with the area but would love to give it a go. I checked the regs, doesn't seem to have many species open besides panfish.  PM me if you would like.  Thanks!
5 feet of snow in a week.. forget it Kevin!
